446
00:30:32,005 --> 00:30:33,005
"Kyungmo"?

447
00:30:34,755 --> 00:30:36,422
"Kyungmo"? Hei, Jaedeok.

448
00:30:37,130 --> 00:30:38,130
Superintenden Go.

449
00:30:38,630 --> 00:30:42,171
Aku yakin kau tak belajar seceroboh ini
saat bersiap untuk ujian hukum.

450
00:30:42,255 --> 00:30:44,130
Kau pasti belajar dengan cermat.

451
00:30:44,213 --> 00:30:46,046
Kenapa kau gagal memeriksa fakta?

452
00:30:46,130 --> 00:30:47,797
Aku tak punya alasan, Pak.

453
